<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Movie Details</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
        }

        li {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .bn {
            border: 2px solid gold;
            background: transparent;
            color: gold;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class='container'>
        <div class="row justify-content-between">
            <div class="mb-5 col">
                <div class="mb-4 display-4 font-weight-bold">John Wick: Chapter 4</div>
                <div class="text-gray-400">
                    <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="list-inline-item mr-3">2023</li>
                        <li class="list-inline-item mr-3">|</li>
                        <li class="list-inline-item">170 Min</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-5 col">
                <div class="h1">
                    <ul class="d-flex">
                        <li><span class="text-warning pb-2">★</span></li>
                        <li>7.7</li>
                        <li><span class="text-muted mr-4">/10</span></li>
                        <li><span class="text-primary">Rate</span></li>
                        <li><span class="text-primary">☆</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row d-flex mb-3">
            <img class='img-fluid mr-4' style='height: 380px; width: 240px; object-fit: cover; object-position: top;' src="~/images/JW.jpg" alt="Poster" />
            <img class='img-fluid' style='height: 380px; width: max-content; object-fit: cover; object-position: top;' src="~/images/JW2.jpg" alt="Backdrop" />
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <button class="bn">Action</button>
            <button class="bn">Thriller</button>
            <button class="bn">Crime</button>
        </div>
        <div class='row'>
            <div class='col-9'>
                <div>
                    <div class='font-weight-bold h4'>
                        Overview :
                    </div>
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        With the price on his head ever increasing, John Wick uncovers a path to defeating The High Table. But before he can earn his freedom, Wick must face off against a new enemy with powerful alliances across the globe and forces that turn old friends into foes.
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <hr />
                        <div class='my-2 d-flex'>
                            <div class='font-weight-bold mr-2'>
                                Director:
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                Chad Stahelski
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr />
                        <div class='my-2 d-flex'>
                            <div class='font-weight-bold mr-2'>
                                Cast :
                            </div>
                            <div class=''>
                                Keanu Reeves
                                Donnie Yen
                                Bill Skarsgård
                                Ian McShane
                                Laurence Fishburne
                                Lance Reddick
                                Clancy Brown
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr />
                        <div class='my-2 d-flex'>
                            <div class='font-weight-bold mr-2'>
                                Tag Line :
                            </div>
                            <div class=''>
                                No way back, one way out.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <hr />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class='col-3 border-left'>
                <div>
                    <div class='font-weight-bold h5'>
                        Status
                    </div>
                    <div class='text-primary'>
                        Released
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class='font-weight-bold h5'>
                        Original Language
                    </div>
                    <div class='text-primary'>
                        English
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class='font-weight-bold h5'>
                        Release Date
                    </div>
                    <div class='text-primary'>
                        2023-03-22
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class='font-weight-bold h5'>
                        Runtime
                    </div>
                    <div class='text-primary'>
                        170 min
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class='position-relative mt-5' style='width: 75%;'>
            <div class='d-flex align-items-center mb-4'>
                <div class="border-left border-warning pl-2">
                    <span class="font-weight-bold h3">Reviews</span>
                    <span class="ml-1">></span>
                </div>
                <div class='position-absolute' style='right: 0;'>
                    <button class='btn btn-primary'>Give Review</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class='mb-4'>
                <div class='d-flex'>
                    <div class='p-4 bg-warning rounded-circle text-center mr-4' style='height: 50px; width: 50px;'>
                        F
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class='font-weight-bold h5'>
                            Floch Forster
                        </div>
                        <div class='text-muted mb-3'>
                            January 7, 2024
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class='d-flex mb-3'>
                    @for (var i = 0; i < 10; i++)
                    {
                        <span class="text-warning">★</span>
                    }
                </div>
                <div>
                    He was the best guy around
                    <hr />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class='mb-4'>
                <div class='d-flex'>
                    <div class='p-4 bg-dark rounded-circle text-center mr-4' style='height: 50px; width: 50px;'>
                        R
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class='font-weight-bold h5'>
                            Reiner Braun
                        </div>
                        <div class='text-muted mb-3'>
                            January 8, 2024
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class='d-flex mb-3'>
                    @for (var i = 0; i < 5; i++)
                    {
                        <span class="text-warning">★</span>
                    }
                    @for (var i = 0; i < 5; i++)
                    {
                        <span class="text-muted">☆</span>
                    }
                </div>
                <div>
                    What about the people he.....?
                    <hr />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class='d-flex justify-content-center'>
                <button class='btn btn-primary'>Show More</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
